div.p: CPU privilege level change via TSS on interrupt/syscall

g.text: 2. Saves user SS:ESP to kernel stack
4. Pushes CS:EIP, EFLAGS to kernel stack

div.p: 0xC00FEEE0: SS (0x23) ESP 0xC00FEEE4: ESP (0xBFFFF000) 0xC00FEEE8: EFLAGS 0xC00FEEEC: CS (0x1B) 0xC00FEF00: EIP (user_code) 0xC00FEF04: (error code if any) --- bottom of kernel stack ---
